The '''''Out of Touch''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|ship]] owned by [[Tok-Foge Pokresh]] and registered on [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]] with registration number RN40-844033. In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]], it was one of many ships [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] tracked as they passed the inner flight control buoys of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Teyr/Legends|Teyr]].

